<item>
            <title>[SEC-1077] AuthenticationProcessingFilter doesn&apos;t redirect to target url in case of session-fixation &quot;newSession&quot;.</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-1077</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When session-fixation-protection=&quot;newSession&quot; is used then AbstractProcessingFilter processing filter doesn&apos;t redirect to target url. It is because of saved request clearing in session (2.0.4, trunk).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="25304">SEC-1077</key>
            <summary>AuthenticationProcessingFilter doesn&apos;t redirect to target url in case of session-fixation &quot;newSession&quot;.</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.spring.io/images/icons/issuetypes/bug.png">Bug</type>
